# Source of truth

1. Current conversation
2. Current code
3. Platform docs (Cloudflare, Hono, Vite)
4. `.cursor/docs/` (business requirements + development workflow)
5. `.cursor/tasks/status.md` + active task file
6. `.cursor/memory/lessons.md` (main-agent lessons — see `.cursor/memory/README.md`; prune when noisy)
7. Older tasks only if asked

Docs, tasks, and memory never override (1)–(3). Main agent owns
`status.md` — see `.cursor/rules/main-agent.mdc`.
